title: Bug 109350: Output parameter not displayed in data set dialog
OB: Output parameter is not displayed in the data set dialog when calling the stored procedure from the Oracle database.
EB: The output parameter should be displayed in the data set dialog when the stored procedure is called from the Oracle database.
SR:
Steps to reproduce:
1. Call the stored procedure from the Oracle database.
2. Check the data set dialog to verify if the output parameter is displayed.
